highlights.text: Metro Boomin has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Creepin' (with The Weeknd & 21 Savage)” is the highest at #3.
“Bloody Mary” by Lady Gaga is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 148 spots at #31.
“Creepin' (with The Weeknd & 21 Savage)” by Metro Boomin, The Weeknd, and 21 Savage is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #3.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 305 weeks straight.
